grab a pencil off of the cabinet on the right
turn around and walk to the end of the room where the black chair is, then turn right and walk to the end of the room where the lamp is on the small table
place the pencil down on the small table next to the lamp

high_descs: Turn left and head towards the dresser.

Turn around, head towards the door, and then turn right to face the lamp on the table.
Place the pen  to the right of the lamp.

high_descs: Head across the room to the counter with the plant.
Pick up the pen from the counter.
Turn around and bring the pen around the other side of the bed to the small round table.
Put the pen on the round table.
